\pard\plain \ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0 \~In pains and in anxieties do you bear (children),\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/15687b.htm"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b1 woman}}{\f0\fs24\b0 ; and toward your husband (is) your inclination, and he lords it over you.\~And do you not\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/08673a.htm"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b1 know}}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~that you are (each) an Eve? The sentence of God on this sex of yours lives in this age: the guilt must of necessity live too.\~}{\f0\fs24\b0\i1 You}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~are the\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/04764a.htm"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b1 devil's}}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~gateway:\~}{\f0\fs24\b0\i1 you}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~are the unsealer of that (forbidden) tree:\~}{\f0\fs24\b0\i1 you}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~are the first deserter of the\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/09071a.htm"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b1 divine law}}{\f0\fs24\b0 :\~}{\f0\fs24\b0\i1 you}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~are she who persuaded him whom the\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/04764a.htm"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b1 devil}}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~was not valiant enough to attack.\~}{\f0\fs24\b0\i1 You}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~destroyed so easily God's image, man. On account of\~}{\f0\fs24\b0\i1 your}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~desert \hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0  that is, death \hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0  even the\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/14142b.htm"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b1 Son of God}}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~had to die. And do you think about adorning yourself over and above your tunics of skins? Come, now; if from the beginning of the world the Milesians sheared sheep, and the Serians spun trees, and the Tyrians dyed, and the Phrygians embroidered with the needle, and the\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/02179b.htm"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b1 Babylonians}}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~with the loom, and pearls gleamed, and onyx-stones flashed; if gold itself also had already issued, with the cupidity (which accompanies it), from the ground; if the mirror, too, already had licence to lie so largely, Eve, expelled from paradise, (Eve) already dead, would also have\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/04462a.htm"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b1 coveted}}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~}{\f0\fs24\b0\i1 these}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~things, I\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/07672a.htm"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b1 imagine}}{\f0\fs24\b0 ! No more, then, ought she\~}{\f0\fs24\b0\i1 now}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~to crave, or be acquainted with (if she desires to live again), what, when she\~}{\f0\fs24\b0\i1 was}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~living, she had neither had nor\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/08673a.htm"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b1 known}}{\f0\fs24\b0 . Accordingly these things are all the baggage of\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/15687b.htm"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b1 woman}}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~in her condemned and dead state, instituted as if to swell the pomp of her funeral.}{ }
\par\plain 
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 is not only not to be desired, but even execrated, by you: first, because the study of making personal\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/06689a.htm"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b1 grace}}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~(which we\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/08673a.htm"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b1 know}}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~to be naturally the inviter of\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/09438a.htm"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b1 lust}}{\f0\fs24\b0 ) a mean of pleasing does not spring from a sound\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/04268a.htm"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b1 conscience}}{\f0\fs24\b0 : why therefore excite toward yourself that\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/05649a.htm"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b1 evil}}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~(passion)? Why invite (that) to which you profess yourself a stranger? Secondly, because we ought not to open a way to\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/14504a.htm"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b1 temptations}}{\f0\fs24\b0 , which, by their instancy, sometimes achieve (a\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/05649a.htm"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b1 wickedness}}{\f0\fs24\b0 ) which\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/06608a.htm"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b1 God}}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~expels from them who are His; (or,) at all events, put the spirit into a thorough tumult by (presenting) a stumbling-block (to it).}{ }
